<varlistentry id="options.FirstTry">
	<term>FirstTry <emphasis remap='I'>SmartPlacement|RandomPlacement|Tile</emphasis></term>
	<listitem>
		<para>strategy to use while placing window. The FirstTry strategy
        will attempt to place window in empty space only.</para>
		<para>See Also: <ulink url="Placement#synopsis">Window Placement types</ulink> for further details.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
